Title: Alexis Goodlooking and the Case of the Missing Whisky
Plot: In order to hide his relationship with Lynn, Frank convinces his mother that he is dating Liz. Tracy and Jenna team up to try to solve the case of Pete's missing whisky. Meanwhile, Jack teaches Kenneth how to take down his first business nemesis.
GuestStars: Stanley Tucci, Patti LuPone, Susan Sarandon
